                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="16900031" author="q79969786" created="Mon, 5 Aug 2019 12:01:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;cc &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=maxgekk&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;maxgekk&quot;&gt;maxgekk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16900059" author="maxgekk" created="Mon, 5 Aug 2019 12:50:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=yumwang&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;yumwang&quot;&gt;yumwang&lt;/a&gt; Thanks. I will take a look at the issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16900083" author="maxgekk" created="Mon, 5 Aug 2019 13:27:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The problem is in storing values of DATE type to a hive table. The values (days since epoch) are converted to java.sql.Date, and after that serialized to string by hive-exec &lt;b&gt;using Date.toString() which is wrong&lt;/b&gt;, see the attached screenshot.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16900090" author="maxgekk" created="Mon, 5 Aug 2019 13:33:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just in case, the issue exists for negative years storing to Hive tables only. Such years are out of valid range for DATE/TIMESTAMP types.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17072694" author="q79969786" created="Wed, 1 Apr 2020 12:06:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=maxgekk&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;maxgekk&quot;&gt;maxgekk&lt;/a&gt; collect() also returns incorrect result:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;image-wrap&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12998451/12998451_collect+make_date.png&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px solid black&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17080303" author="q79969786" created="Fri, 10 Apr 2020 07:29:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is because of &lt;tt&gt;toJavaDate&lt;/tt&gt;:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/blob/bb295d80e37440e6ee67a00bc09df2e9ff6e4e46/sql/catalyst/src/main/scala/org/apache/spark/sql/catalyst/util/DateTimeUtils.scala#L107-L116&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/blob/bb295d80e37440e6ee67a00bc09df2e9ff6e4e46/sql/catalyst/src/main/scala/org/apache/spark/sql/catalyst/util/DateTimeUtils.scala#L107-L116&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;scala&amp;gt;       val d1 = java.time.LocalDate.ofEpochDay(-735525)
d1: java.time.LocalDate = -0044-03-15

scala&amp;gt;       java.sql.Date.valueOf(d1)
res12: java.sql.Date = 0045-03-15
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17080312" author="maxgekk" created="Fri, 10 Apr 2020 07:46:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;toJavaDate is implemented differently in the master&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/blob/e2d9399602d485eae94cd530d134ebab336e9e9b/sql/catalyst/src/main/scala/org/apache/spark/sql/catalyst/util/DateTimeUtils.scala#L129-L132&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/blob/e2d9399602d485eae94cd530d134ebab336e9e9b/sql/catalyst/src/main/scala/org/apache/spark/sql/catalyst/util/DateTimeUtils.scala#L129-L132&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17125345" author="apachespark" created="Wed, 3 Jun 2020 21:42:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;User &apos;MaxGekk&apos; has created a pull request for this issue:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/28721&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/28721&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
